node.text:
Our 12 Days of Giving starts now! We’re kicking off the giving by helping you bring the essence of Pure Salt to your home this holiday season! Like with any of our projects, that means leaning in to design that is cozy, fresh, clean (in every sense), and inspired to create a natural atmosphere where cherished memories are made. We think every home needs a little bit of:
- cozy music
- candles & scents
- calm & clean decor
- candles, candles, and more candles!
Check out our stories today to learn more about how we use each element to infuse the season with some Pure Salt magic ✨// 🎬: @trevorfilm

node.text: Dipping our toes into video content with @618studios to tell you a little bit more about who we are and what makes us Pure Salt!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pure Salt Interiors on August 19, 2021. May be an image of furniture and bedroom.

node.text:
This? Or that? We're playing our favorite game on stories today, & this time it's Bedding Edition! Do you prefer the Riptide duvet stripe side up or down? Which kilim headboard piques your interest? Play along and let us know your faves, we can't wait to see the winners✨ // 📷: @vlentine

node.text:
We're still dreaming about our #northtustinproject kitchen and this AM we thought we'd reminisce through photo! That hand painted tile backsplash is what dreams are made of! And our Elliot pendants sure do make a statement and complement all the natural light from the home's many windows and skylights✨And speaking of complements, we love the Hale Navy island! It really pops against all the white cabinetry //⁣
 📷: @vlentine⁣
🏠: @forehanconstruction

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pure Salt Interiors in Rancho Mission Viejo. May be an image of furniture and living room.

node.text:
Have you met our best seller Lolesa? She's our start pendant and we love that still looks incredible, even when she's not center stage✨⁣
⁣
And for all of you who have been asking after these chairs and cushions, they are on the shoppe! Click the tag in the photo to shop // 📷: @vlentine

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pure Salt Interiors in Los Gatos, California. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: So much natural light and fresh whites make this spa-like master bath at our #losgatosproject shine and sing✨we love this photo for illustrating how this room really draws you eye along the texture—from the reeded glass, to the leaning mirrors and wood vanity, to the pendant over the tub, there is so much goodness to see in this space! // 📷: @vlentine

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pure Salt Interiors in Rancho Mission Viejo with @slightlychoppy, and @littlesaltshoppe. May be an image of bedroom.

node.text: We are leveling up! With our raw hem Logan bedding, Reef pillow, and @slightlychoppy flags, My son JP's room is feeling beachy and totally cool. I love that i can layer and mix and match these pieces to keep things fresh and inspired for him as he grows🤍// 📷: @vlentine

node.text: This cozy view of our #portstreetsproject living room is everything✨ our elm coffee table and vintage rug add great texture, our sectional and stacks of fave shoppe pillows bring in the softness, and all the pops of greenery make the space feel so lively! // 📷: @vlentine

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pure Salt Interiors in Rancho Mission Viejo. May be an image of furniture and bedroom.

node.text: Getting a dreamy bedroom looks is easy when you follow our bedding essentials checklist! Add one of our reversible duvets for double the possibilities, stack some of our go-to pillows, and add calming decor and lighting for ambiance✨check out everything you need to know on stories this afternoon, plus our step by step guide on how to make a Pure Salt bed on Grain of Salt! // 📷: @vlentine

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pure Salt Interiors in Los Gatos, California with @littlesaltshoppe. May be an image of indoor.

node.text:
No Sunday scaries here 🙅‍♀️ just sunny desk views as we gear up for this amazing week ahead and our littles jump into a brand new school year✨ ⁣
⁣
That being said, happy back to school to all the mamas out there! We're sending all our hopes and wishes for a great year for our kiddos // 📷: @vlentine

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Pure Salt Interiors on August 14, 2021 tagging @hannahbrown. May be an image of bedroom.

node.text:
Another reason to fall in love with our new bedding collection? All the duvets are reversible! We love having options when styling a space, and no room changes as much as our bedrooms—we need things to always feel fresh and new! Seen here in #hannahshouseproject our Cliffside duvet has a subtle, pretty pinstripe on one side, and the coziest taupe on the other. We love it when we can have the best of both worlds✨ // 📷: @vlentine

node.text: A moment of respite from all these killer bedrooms with this gorgeous guest bathroom ☁ with white cabinets in the vanity and complementing white oak door and mirror, it's the simple things that make this bathroom sing // 📷: @vlentine

node.text: Quiet bedroom built-ins are our favorite way to display personal and sentimental decor mixed with beautiful pieces✨ It's about layering family treasures with accessories you can swap in and out as moods or seasons change, so your space always feels fresh and rejuvinated // 📷: @vlentine
